# Module: `excalidraw-app`

- App-level concerns only (routing, persistence, collaboration)
- Do not duplicate logic already in `packages/excalidraw` — import instead
- Firebase and Socket.io usage is confined to this package

## How to verify

- `grep -r "firebase\|socket.io" packages/` — should return nothing (app-only)
- `grep -r "from.*packages/excalidraw" excalidraw-app/` — imports must go through `@excalidraw/excalidraw`, not direct paths
